Snake SDL2 - Revolutionary Edition
A revolutionary take on the classic Snake game with magical powers,
spectacular visual effects, and modern C++ architecture.

Features:
- 7 types of magical foods with unique effects
- Advanced particle system and visual effects  
- Combo system with score multipliers
- Achievement system with 30+ achievements
- Progressive difficulty levels
- Power-ups: Speed Boost, Double Score, Phase Mode, and more!
- Modern C++ architecture with RAII memory management
- Cross-platform SDL2 implementation

Enjoy the most revolutionary Snake experience ever created!